          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Telescopes consisted of silicon neutron",
                " -alloyed E detectors with the thickness of 1.5 mm and",
                "silicon surface-barrier delta-E detectors with the",
                "thickness of 50-70 mu-m were placed on two independent",
                "platforms: one detector at the left and the other two",
                "detectors at the right from the beam. Diaphragms (6 mm",
                "in diameter) were placed immediately in front of delta-",
                "E detectors at the distance of 150-200 mm from the",
                "target. Solid angles were tested on counting rates in",
                "peaks of deuteron elastic scattering on titanium,",
                "tritium and carbon nuclei."
              ]
            }
          ],
